Q1_1: Cognitive Load - Mental Demand: How mentally demanding was the task?
Q1_2: Cognitive Load - Physical Demand: How physically demanding was the task?
Q1_3: Cognitive Load - Temporal Demand: How hurried or rushed was the pace of the task?
Q1_4: Cognitive Load - Performance: How successful were you in accomplishing what you were asked to do?
Q1_5: Cognitive Load - Effort: How hard did you have to work to accomplish your level of performance?
Q1_6: Cognitive Load - Frustration: How insecure, discouraged, irritated, stressed, and annoyed were you?
Q5_1: User Confidence - How confident are you in your evaluation?
